923
00:40:13.823 --> 00:40:17.603
Whoo!

924
00:40:19.282 --> 00:40:21.670
Oh. my God!

925
00:40:21.670 --> 00:40:23.304
Oh. my God!

926
00:40:23.304 --> 00:40:25.248
