970
00:42:10.406 --> 00:42:12.895
Um. nit-- nitroglycerin.

971
00:42:12.895 --> 00:42:14.869
Yes!
Nitroglycerin.

972
00:42:14.869 --> 00:42:18.011
Nitroglycerin is a
colourless liquid that's used

973
00:42:18.011 --> 00:42:21.744
