to manufacture explosives.

974
00:42:21.744 --> 00:42:23.347
Oh. yeah!
(chuckling)

975
00:42:23.347 --> 00:42:26.065
This is a very.
very interesting chemical.

976
00:42:26.065 --> 00:42:28.697
