1016
00:44:01.748 --> 00:44:05.274
You know. Bobby. sometimes
people are douchebags

1017
00:44:05.274 --> 00:44:06.896
just to make
themselves feel better.

1018
00:44:06.896 --> 00:44:08.910
It has nothing to do with you.

1019
00:44:09.847 --> 00:44:10.916
