1020
00:44:10.916 --> 00:44:12.089
Keys?

1021
00:44:12.089 --> 00:44:13.151
Like house keys.

1022
00:44:13.151 --> 00:44:14.067
Yeah. yeah. Yeah.

1023
00:44:14.067 --> 00:44:15.593
Let me show you a little trick
my mom taught me

1024
00:44:15.593 --> 00:44:17.004
