Hey! Miss Del Rio!

1036
00:44:37.978 --> 00:44:40.103
Hey. Coach Chuck!
Big win last night.

1037
00:44:40.103 --> 00:44:41.231
Congratulations.

1038
00:44:41.231 --> 00:44:43.069
I gotta say. I saw how you
