You're funny.

1042
00:44:48.327 --> 00:44:49.324
You should see me naked.

1043
00:44:49.324 --> 00:44:50.551
(chuckling)
Really?

1044
00:44:50.551 --> 00:44:51.501
You know what. Coach?

1045
00:44:51.501 --> 00:44:53.187
